(secondQuint)Efficacy of Music Therapy Protocols for Burn Debridement.

 The study is a prospective, randomized crossover clinical trial conducted on a 14-bed inpatient comprehensive burn care center.

 The purpose of this study is to investigate the efficacy of Music-Based Imagery (MBI) and Music Alternate Engagement (MAE) for pain and anxiety management for burn patients throughout the debridement process.

